commit.message:
alloc-pool.c, [...]: Update copyright.

	* alloc-pool.c, except.h, ggc-common.c, ggc-zone.c, ggc.h,
	stringpool.c, config/mips/mips-protos.h: Update copyright.

From-SVN: r96428
